<dita>
   <concept id="FAR_29_401_3" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">29.401-3</ph> Federal, State, and local taxes.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d1860e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1883e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            Except as provided in paragraph (b) of this section, insert the clause at <xref href="52.229-3.dita#FAR_52_229_3"
                        base="i1051470"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.229-3</xref>, Federal, State, and Local Taxes, in solicitations and contracts if-</p>
               <ol id="d1860e26" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d1883e19">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
								                The contract is to be performed wholly or partly in the United States or its outlying areas;</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d1883e24">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
								                A fixed-price contract is contemplated; and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d1883e29">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
								                The contract is expected to exceed the simplified acquisition threshold.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1883e34">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            In a noncompetitive contract that meets all the conditions in paragraph (a) of this section, the contracting officer may insert the clause at <xref href="52.229-4.dita#FAR_52_229_4"
                        base="i1051494"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.229-4</xref>, Federal, State, and Local Taxes (State and Local Adjustments), instead of the clause at <xref href="52.229-3.dita#FAR_52_229_3"
                        base="i1051470"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.229-3</xref>, if the price would otherwise include an inappropriate contingency for potential postaward change(s) in State or local taxes.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
</dita>
